text: Abraham Viktor Rydberg (born 18 December 1828 in Jönköping, Sweden, died 21 September 1895 in Djursholm, Sweden) was a Swedish writer. Between 1877-1895 he was a member of the Swedish Academy. == References == Category:1828 births Category:1895 deaths Category:Swedish writers Category:People from Jönköping
title: Viktor Rydberg
